Author: mrSprinkles
Title: ⛏ StartMining ICO has already started!⛏
Body: ICO has already started!  Right now you can buy tokens at http://ico.startmining.com  We accept: Bitcoin, Ethereum, Wire Transfer (bank transfer).  Smart Contract Address: 0xe8Da050C3140183D4f5F01E048aC136e2DA5253f  In the first 24 hours a 25% bonus is available!  Our 24/7 support provides assistance in Telegram and by email pay@startmining.com.   StartMining - is a unique project that is based on a construction and launching of the largest industrial mining farms in Russia and Europe. It is planned to build platforms with the overall capacity up to 4,000 farms. The main sources of company’s income:  Mining the main cryptocurrencies: Ethereum, Zcash and Monero Provision of mining facilities as rental (cloud mining)   StartMining goals    Milestones    Investor's benefits   Investments legalization and “white” taxation The highest profit – 40% of the company’s net profit with revenue up to 122% per year For example: if you invest $100, you will be able to receive $122 as dividends within 1 year, and your investment worth of 100 stmg will be persisted The first token supported by real equipment and facilities Minimization of risks by the diversification of cryptocurrencies and provision of facilities as rental Open access to the current farms’ output Possibility to exchange tokens on mining facilities - real asset Launching terms are no longer than 4 months One of the lowest electricity costs (up to 2 cents/KW) Wholesale prices for equipment and components   StartMining Team      What is a Start Mining token?  StartMining token equals to company’s share. It is supported by real mining equipment and facilities. Token guarantees the right to participate in the distribution of the company's profits and may be converted into real assets.   Limited number of tokens 10 200 000 tokens. 93% of tokens are issued to realize initial ICO goals; 2% — Bounty program and bonuses; 5% — Escrow.   Regulation All unrealized tokens will be burned.  Initial token price  $1  ICO course 18.09.2017 - 17.10.2017 (30 calendar days)  Financial goals 500 000 $ - $ 10,000,000  Accepted currencies ETH, Altcoins, USD/EUR, Visa/MasterCard  StartMining ICO platform Ethereum smart-contract (ERC20)  Escrow participates in the project.   Social networks and other information:  Whitepaper: http://startmining.com/whitepaper_eng.pdf Website: http://startmining.com/ Bounty program: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2135183.0 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/startmining.official Twitter: https://twitter.com/startmining_com YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZl3jQkc_gNgXphb-Dc3-6A Telegram: https://t.me/startmining_com Infographics: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VvEVnCRTQY0 Slack: https://startmining-ico.slack.com/
